<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>131</hymn_number>
<title>Piga Sana Vita Vyema TZR131</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Piga sana vita vyema
 Kwa ushujaa daima,
 Yesu ndiye nguvu zako,
 Yesu ndiye kweli yako.

[V2]
 Kaza mwendo, ushindane
 Angaza macho, umwone
 Yesu ndiye njia yako,
 Naye ndiye tuzo lako.

[V3]
 Tupa kizito, simama,
 Tazama mbele, si nyuma;
 Ni yeye uzima wako,
 Naye ni kipendo chako.

[V4]
 Tangamka, uamini
 Akushika mikononi
 Hageuki, akupenda,
 Kuwa naye una pia.</lyrics>
</song>